{"tid":1678772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【各區示威】催淚煙飄入九巴車廂　乘客：無諗過喺咁多乘客前放催淚彈","createTime":"2019-10-27T23:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T13:03:02.000Z","uid":252013,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8f464286b89ec1a3220b31a4e37d69814340e1","tid":1678772,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚（27日）深夜在油尖旺清場期間，在彌敦道近亞皆老街一架905號巴士前施放催淚彈，車廂內的車長及乘客隨即掩鼻，車長因吸入催淚煙感到不適。一名坐在該巴士上層的乘客嚴小姐表示，已習慣警方的行動，亦預料今晚油尖旺會有警察，但「無諗過佢哋喺咁多個乘客前面都會放催淚彈」，巴士當時隨即停下，乘客下車。<br />\n嚴小姐稱，此前已聞過催淚煙，今次沒感到很不舒服，但目睹巴士上一名女乘客在哭，「不滿（警察）就一定，更不滿是不止催淚煙，還有四處都留有殘留物」。<br />\n今（28日）凌晨零時過後，警方於旺角銀行中...<a href=\"https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=131160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwl%26id%3D131160&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4SHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=bc6e4091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.klwpc.com/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=131160</a>"},{"pid":"76a7becd4d75694cb69b5f0f7800e30f0660be5a","tid":1678772,"uid":152293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCrbQS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCrbQS6.jpg&h=a5576e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igSRQS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigSRQS6.jpg&h=31293e91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0678f428c4e2d344da6cae82d9847f223151a767","tid":1678772,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76a7becd4d75694cb69b5f0f7800e30f0660be5a","tid":1678772,"uid":152293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCrbQS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCrbQS6.jpg&h=a5576e38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igSRQS6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigSRQS6.jpg&h=31293e91&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Mfv6t9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Mfv6t9.jpg&h=29478751&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pS6EO9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pS6EO9.jpg&h=35304234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"969ae4ab2dca717e381b6dc1c357e46db93a7689","tid":1678772,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:29:04.000Z","msg":"啲狗會諸多藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e16a3a64dfdb04b2184aecefcbb44bce1ab454","tid":1678772,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:39:52.000Z","msg":"bingo 紙：係電光火石間作出專業克制既保護乘客行動"},{"pid":"e5dcc0b085f3c73d2e929715467e342f1d966f04","tid":1678772,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:40:01.000Z","msg":"10月27號 旺角 黑警包抄包得好犀利<br />\n1衝鋒車打頭陣 2～3豬籠車跟尾<br />\n(☝🏻直接揸車衝入嚟裝修鋪頭/目的地/一班手足逃忙緊附近馬路 呢種游擊戰術之前見過)<br />\n今日嘅分別係堆車差唔多埋位之濟 黑警左右街口夾埋嚟 係差在彌敦道條直路未包抄埋 <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">彌敦道頭冇車冇人<br />\n<br />\n左邊防暴衝過嚟 被裝修鋪頭 右邊防暴衝過黎<br />\n<br />\n彌敦道尾衝鋒車豬籠車</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">解決方法 </span></span><br />\n裝修時間縮短 <br />\n完成目標即刻走唔好戀戰 <br />\n尤其係銀行會即時連接狗屋呢類<br />\n同時唔排除班狗mon住所有直播頻道 <br />\n即係話裝修開始一刻 班狗已經知道目的地<br />\n繼而出車實行包抄<br />\n<br />\n班狗車一衝埋嚟一落車已經有目標咁捉人 眼見有咩袋 除咗衫白色 其他balck bloc 黑口罩帶帽企埋一邊班黑警都無視"},{"pid":"024ce9b6f9c79a0aa3b2f43f03ffea9639edb918","tid":1678772,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"未訓醒？"},{"pid":"04